fields.name: Air Max 95 OG Neon
fields.description: The 2020 Nike Air Max 95 retro is as OG as its 1995 debut. The original design was based on the human body, specifically the ribcage. Keeping up with the ribcage inspiration, the upper features its quintessential ripple makeup, stacking suede in a gradient pattern. Pops of neon green appear throughout from the air bubbles to the miniature Swoosh logo on the ankle. Reflective detailing is featured on the heel and tongue, making this a true OG return.

fields.name: Air Max 95 OG Crystal Blue
fields.description: The Nike Air Max 95 OG Crystal Blue showcases a gradient of gray on the paneled upper as hits of blue on the tongue, lancelets, and lining work together to decorate Sergio Lozano's signature look. Meanwhile, the midsole is designed in black and hosts blue-tinted Air pockets, and the outsole unit reveals n AM95 PSI. The sneaker showcases white mesh on most parts, including the outsole, Max Air sole unit, eyelets, Swoosh logos, and blue accents on the tongue lining. Moreover, the rubber outsole imitates the black midsole to round out the significant features of the sneaker.

fields.name: Air Max 95 OG Black Anthracite
fields.description: The upper of the OG Black Anthracite Nike Air Max 95 is crafted from a blend of premium leather, mesh, and synthetic materials. The heel includes a visible Air Max unit to provide optimal cushioning for high-impact activities. The shoe also boasts Nike branding, with the Swoosh logo on the lateral and medial sides and the Nike Air logo on the heel. Additionally, the shoe has reflective detailing throughout. The outsole is made of rubber for enhanced grip.

fields.name: Air Max 95 OG Solar Red
fields.description: One of the most popular Air Max silhouettes of all time, the Nike Air Max 95 is back in an OG colorway. Last releasing in 2011, the Solar Red colorway is back in original fashion. This pair utilizes a white, solar red, granite, and dust color palette. The unique Air Max 95 model, designed by Sergio Lozano, draws inspiration from the human-anatomy. This pair released for $160 in July 2018.

fields.name: Air Max 95 OG Fresh Mint
fields.description: Get fresher than a mint and cop the Air Max 95 OG Fresh Mint. This AM 95 comes with a grey upper plus white and mint accents, mint Nike 'Swoosh', black midsole, and a black sole. These sneakers released in May 2019 and retailed for $160. Grab these fresh kicks on StockX now.

fields.name: Air Max 90 Infrared
fields.description: The Nike Air Max 90 Infrared arrives in a mix of white mesh, black leather, and grey suede with Infrared inserts on the midfoot, heel tab, and mudguard. A white Air bubble, classic Nike Air branding on the heel tab, and a black and Infrared sole complete the retro design.

fields.name: Air Max 90 Laser Blue
fields.description: Fans of the classic Nike Air Max 90 model will love everything about this colorway’s return. The upper is constructed of white leather with grey suede Swoosh and a black mudguard. Hits of Laser Blue appear throughout to give the sneaker it’s signature look.

fields.name: Air Max 90 OG Volt
fields.description: This OG Air Max 90 by Nike has an upper dressed in white mesh with gray suede overlays and a black leather mudguard. The shoe sits atop a foam midsole with visible Air sole cushioning. Energetic pops of Volt deliver contrasting color at the eyestay, heel and also at the midsole wedge.

fields.name: Air Max 90 Grape
fields.description: This sneaker features an upper made of a White mesh base with Grey suede overlays, Black leather mudguard, and Hyper Grape accents on the tongue branding, some parts of the outsole, the heel tab with Nike branding, the side panels with ‘Air Max’ branding, a section of the midsole with a visible Air unit, and the front TPU eyestays. A White midsole and a Black waffle rubber outsole round out the design.

fields.name: Air Max 90 Triple Black
fields.description: The Leather Triple Nike Air Max 90 Black 2020 has a midsole that is equipped with Nike's patented Air Max technology, providing maximum comfort and cushioning with each step. The air unit is visible through the outsole of the shoe. The outsole of the sneaker features a waffle pattern that provides excellent traction and grip on various surfaces.

fields.name: Air Max 1 Anniversary Royal
fields.description: This Nike Air Max 1 is dressed in its OG color scheme of White, Sport Royal, and Neutral Grey. The Sport Royal accent is visible on the Swoosh, upper eyelets, suede mudguard, and Nike branding on the tongue and heels. Other details include white mesh paneling, grey suede, white midsole, and black detailing on the outsole. The Air unit is placed within the heel to finish off the design.

fields.name: Air Max 1 Anniversary Red
fields.description: The 2017 Restock Air Max 1 design features a nubuck and mesh contrasting upper with Neutral Grey, University Red and crisp white panels. The simple color palette continues via the red Nike branding and the white Air Max sole unit, which is capped off with a red, black and white outsole. Finally, two sets of white laces in matte and satin finish round out the pair.

fields.name: Air Max 1 Anniversary Orange
fields.description: The Nike Air Max 1 Anniversary Orange features similar color blocking styles to its OG Red and Royal Blue colorways. The upper is constructed out of orange and grey synthetic suede. Hits of black peek through on the outsole while a white midsole brings together the classic design.

fields.name: Air Max 1 Anniversary Green
fields.description: The Nike Air Max 1 Anniversary Green (2020) features a white, Evergreen Aura, and gray leather and mesh upper, with white acting as a background that feeds into Evergreen Aura mudguards and gray overlays. From there, an 'Air Max' midsole with exposed pods sits atop a two-toned outsole and slight black accents for bordering to complete the design.

fields.name: Air Max TN Plus Hyper Blue
fields.description: The first thing that draws your eye on the retro is the yellow mini-Swoosh, popping from its usual sidewall position. Moving onto the back, the hexagonal “Tn AIR” logo is stamped onto the heel, beckoning out as bright as it did during its ‘98 release. The canvas upper details the iconic gradient, moving from a dark blue to white, with the black welded lines representing the shadowed palm trees that designer Sean McDowell was inspired by. As per usual, the Whale Bone feature sits in the centre of the sole unit between the front and rear Air bags, providing torsional support and stability.

fields.name: Air Max TN Plus Tiger
fields.description: The Nike Air Max Plus Tiger is a stylish and comfortable sneaker that features a bold tiger stripe pattern on the upper. The shoe is made with a combination of synthetic and textile materials, providing durability and breathability. The iconic Air Max cushioning technology in the sole ensures a comfortable ride, while the rubber outsole provides traction and durability. The colorway of the shoe is predominantly black and orange, with white accents on the midsole and Nike branding

fields.name: Air Max TN Plus 25th Anniversary
fields.description: Celebrating 25 years of bold design, the Nike Air Max Plus '25th Anniversary' edition pays homage to this trailblazing ‘90s sneaker. Tying together an assortment of fan-favourite colourways, this pair is truly a celebration of the globally renowned silhouette.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Chicago (2015)
fields.description: The Jordan 1 Retro Chicago (2015) features white, red, and black premium leather uppers with white panels used as a base, Varsity Red overlays wrapping around it, and deep black hues rounding out the Nike 'Swooshes' and other accents. From there, a minimal 'Nike Air logo and a red outsole to match the traditional colors of the famous Chicago Bulls complete the design.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Taxi
fields.description: This Retro OG Air Jordan 1 comes in an all leather build that combines a white base with a yellow toe box, and some yellow overlays in the heel and ankle area. A contrasting black appears in the toe and lace area, Swoosh, and Wings logo on the lateral side. A classic AJ1 white midsole and a yellow rubber outsole round off the design.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Blue Moon
fields.description: The Blue Moon Air Jordan 1s are part of Nikes Best Hand in the Game pack and are a royal flush for any fit. These shoes come in a summit white, blue moon and black colorway, offering another twist on the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Black Toe.' These Js feature a white and black-based upper with blue suede accents and a straight flush on the right insole. These dropped in May of 2018, where they were only available at select Jordan Brand retailers in North America. These are must-have for fans of the AJ 1 and of Jordans many historical achievements.

fields.name: Air Jordan 1 Pine Green
fields.description: The Blue Moon Air Jordan 1s are part of Nikes Best Hand in the Game pack and are a royal flush for any fit. These shoes come in a summit white, blue moon and black colorway, offering another twist on the Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Black Toe.' These Js feature a white and black-based upper with blue suede accents and a straight flush on the right insole. These dropped in May of 2018, where they were only available at select Jordan Brand retailers in North America. These are must-have for fans of the AJ 1 and of Jordans many historical achievements.

fields.name: Nike Air Force 1 White Low '07
fields.description: The Nike Air Force 1 Low White ‘07 features an all-white leather upper with a perforated toe box and Swoosh overlays. A Nike heel embroidery and white sole completes the design.

fields.name: Nike Air Force 1 Black Low '07
fields.description: The Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 Black features a triple black smooth leather upper with a matching Air sole and laces. Subtle Nike Air embroidery on the heel tab nods to the history of the AF-1 line. A metallic lace tag and woven tongue label complete the design.

fields.name: Air Huarache Triple Black
fields.description: The Nike Air Huarache Triple Black 2021 is entirely made up of synthetic leather and a nylon combo that is paired to the neoprene bootie. The sneaker also features a flexible molded heel structure. This sneaker’s entire upper part is made up of an encapsulated Air unit. The entire sneaker is black colored.

fields.name: Air Huarache White Pure Platinum
fields.description: The Nike Air Huarache White Pure Platinum 2021 is a sleek and stylish sneaker that combines comfort and performance. The upper is made of a breathable mesh material that provides ventilation and support, while the neoprene inner sleeve offers a snug and comfortable fit. The white and pure platinum colorway gives the shoe a clean and modern look that is perfect for any occasion.

fields.name: Nike Dunk Low Retro Panda
fields.description: The Nike Air Huarache White Pure Platinum 2021 is a sleek and stylish sneaker that combines comfort and performance. The upper is made of a breathable mesh material that provides ventilation and support, while the neoprene inner sleeve offers a snug and comfortable fit. The white and pure platinum colorway gives the shoe a clean and modern look that is perfect for any occasion.

fields.name: Nike Dunk Low Nike Dunk Low Clear Jade
fields.description: The Clear Jade Nike Dunk Low-Top features a white leather upper with a perforated toebox for breathability. Clear Jade leather is used for the side panel Nike Swoosh and the overlays surrounding the toebox, eyestays, heel, and collar. The tongue is white with Clear Jade trim, and a white branding patch with Clear Jade Nike branding. The padded sock liner is Clear Jade, and the insole is Clear Jade with white Nike branding. The foam cushion midsole is fully sewn-in and sits atop a rubber cup sole. The outsole is Clear Jade rubber with a traction pattern in concentric circles.​
